rComments: Laurel Besco is a decent lecturer. However, she adds a lot of filler videos, most likely because the course content is dry. Do not waste your money on the textbook, just go to lectures. Bescos wording on her tests is awful, ive had foreign profs with better syntax.

This prof is absolutely amazing and loves helping students. She made the class enjoyable and often told us stories of her travels, which really connected with the content we were learning. I loved her lectures because she encouraged students to think from different perspectives and to voice their opinions. Her grading criteria is extremely clear.
